---

<section id="perche-cambiare" class="py-24 bg-white fade-in">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-16 text-[#DC2626]">
            Perché cambiare i serramenti?
        </h2>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
            <!-- 1. Risparmio Energetico -->
            <div
                class="bg-[#F9FAFB] p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow border-t-4 border-[#DC2626]"
            >
                <div
                    class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-[#DC2626]"
                >
                    <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        fill="none"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        stroke-width="1.5"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        class="w-6 h-6"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            d="M12 3v2.25m6.364.386-1.591 1.591M21 12h-2.25m-.386 6.364-1.591-1.591M12 18.75V21m-4.773-4.227-1.591 1.591M5.25 12H3m4.227-4.773L5.636 5.636M15.75 12a3.75 3.75 0 1 1-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 0 1 7.5 0Z"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-[#111827]">
                    Risparmio Energetico
                </h3>
                <p class="text-[#374151] leading-relaxed">
                    Riduci i consumi fino al 25%. Infissi moderni in PVC o
                    alluminio a taglio termico eliminano le dispersioni,
                    abbassando sensibilmente i costi delle bollette.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- 2. Comfort Abitativo -->
            <div
                class="bg-[#F9FAFB] p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow border-t-4 border-[#DC2626]"
            >
                <div
                    class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-[#DC2626]"
                >
                    <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        fill="none"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        stroke-width="1.5"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        class="w-6 h-6"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            d="M8.25 21v-4.875c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21m0 0h4.5V3.545M12.75 21h7.5V10.75M2.25 21h1.5m18 0h-18M2.25 9l4.5-1.636M18.75 3l-1.5.545m0 6.205 3 1m1.5.5-1.5-.5M6.75 7.364V3h-3v18m3-13.636 10.5-3.819"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-[#111827]">
                    Comfort Abitativo
                </h3>
                <p class="text-[#374151] leading-relaxed">
                    Vivi in un ambiente più silenzioso e accogliente. I doppi o
                    tripli vetri offrono un isolamento acustico superiore e
                    mantengono la temperatura interna stabile.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- 3. Maggiore Sicurezza -->
            <div
                class="bg-[#F9FAFB] p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow border-t-4 border-[#DC2626]"
            >
                <div
                    class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-[#DC2626]"
                >
                    <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        fill="none"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        stroke-width="1.5"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        class="w-6 h-6"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12c0 1.268-.63 2.39-1.593 3.068a3.745 3.745 0 0 1-1.043 3.296 3.745 3.745 0 0 1-3.296 1.043A3.745 3.745 0 0 1 12 21c-1.268 0-2.39-.63-3.068-1.593a3.746 3.746 0 0 1-3.296-1.043 3.745 3.745 0 0 1-1.043-3.296A3.745 3.745 0 0 1 3 12c0-1.268.63-2.39 1.593-3.068a3.745 3.745 0 0 1 1.043-3.296 3.746 3.746 0 0 1 3.296-1.043A3.746 3.746 0 0 1 12 3c1.268 0 2.39.63 3.068 1.593a3.746 3.746 0 0 1 3.296 1.043 3.746 3.746 0 0 1 1.043 3.296A3.745 3.745 0 0 1 21 12Z"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-[#111827]">
                    Maggiore Sicurezza
                </h3>
                <p class="text-[#374151] leading-relaxed">
                    Proteggi la tua famiglia. I serramenti moderni sono dotati
                    di sistemi anti-effrazione avanzati, vetri antisfondamento e
                    ferramenta rinforzata.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- 4. Incentivi Fiscali -->
            <div
                class="bg-[#F9FAFB] p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow border-t-4 border-[#DC2626]"
            >
                <div
                    class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-[#DC2626]"
                >
                    <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        fill="none"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        stroke-width="1.5"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        class="w-6 h-6"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            d="M12 6v12m-3-2.818.879.659c1.171.879 3.07.879 4.242 0 1.172-.879 1.172-2.303 0-3.182C13.536 12.219 12.768 12 12 12c-.725 0-1.45-.22-2.003-.659-1.106-.879-1.106-2.303 0-3.182s2.9-.879 4.006 0l.415.33M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-[#111827]">
                    Incentivi Fiscali
                </h3>
                <p class="text-[#374151] leading-relaxed">
                    Approfitta delle detrazioni. Recupera fino al 50% o 65%
                    della spesa grazie all'Ecobonus e al Bonus Ristrutturazioni.
                </p>
                <a
                    href="#ecobonus"
                    class="inline-block mt-4 text-[#DC2626] font-semibold hover:underline"
                    >Approfondisci →</a
                >
            </div>

            <!-- 5. Valore Immobile -->
            <div
                class="bg-[#F9FAFB] p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow border-t-4 border-[#DC2626] md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-2 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-start"
            >
                <div
                    class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-[#DC2626] flex-shrink-0"
                >
                    <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        fill="none"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        stroke-width="1.5"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        class="w-6 h-6"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            d="M2.25 18 9 11.25l4.306 4.306a11.95 11.95 0 0 1 5.814-5.518l2.74-1.22m0 0-5.94-2.281m5.94 2.28-2.28 5.941"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-[#111827]">
                        Valore dell'Immobile
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-[#374151] leading-relaxed">
                        Un investimento che si rivaluta. L'installazione di
                        infissi di ultima generazione migliora l'efficienza
                        energetica (classe energetica), il design e la sicurezza
                        della tua casa, aumentandone significativamente il
                        valore di mercato e l'attrattiva in caso di vendita.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center mt-12">
            <a
                href="#contatti"
                class="inline-block bg-[#DC2626] hover:bg-red-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-lg font-bold transition-all transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg"
            >
                Richiedi una consulenza gratuita
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
